  <font size=4 color="000080"><b>Administrator Help - Categories Section</b></font><br>
  <hr size=1 noshade>
  This section allows you to manage the auction categories for your entire site.
  <br><br>
  <b>Explanation of page elements</b>

  <br><br>
  <table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=3>
